de.fhluebeck.group3.controller

Class MainFrameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhluebeck.group3.controller.MainFrameController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public final class MainFrameController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    The controller of the main recipe view - MainRecipeFrame.fxml. This controller includes basic view loading functions and logical functions for basic operations on the view. This controller calls the functions from RecipeDAO directly.
    Author:
    Eason.Hua on 2018/05/31.
